DESCRIPTION:Musik\, Tanz\, Drinks und Food im Garten unseres Probenstudios. Gleichzeitig feiern wir unseren Albumrelease "Quirky Nightclub Chronicles".\nEuer arcis (Arcis Saxophon Quartett und arcis_collective)\n\nMusic\, dance\, drinks and food in the garden of our rehearsal studio. At the same time\, we are celebrating the release of our album "Quirky Nightclub Chronicles".\nYour arcis (Arcis Saxophon Quartett and arcis_collective)\n\nKontakt: booking@arcisquartett.de\nWebsite Arcis Saxophon Quartett: https://www.arcissaxophonquartett.de\nWebsite arcis_collective: https://www.arciscollective.de\nInstagram: https://www.instagram.com/arcissaxophonquartett
